Package: GroupHW
Type: Package
Title: Efficient Implementations of K-means, Multiclass Logistic Regression, and LASSO via RcppArmadillo
Version: 1.0
Date: 2020-10-17
Author: Madison Ell [aut], Gayun Kwon [aut], Ritwick Mondal [aut]
Maintainer:  Ritwick Mondal <ritwick12@tamu.edu>
Description: Implements k-means, multiclass logistic regression, and LASSO via proximal gradient with Nesterov acceleration.
  Provides R and C++ backends using RcppArmadillo, along with tests and timing utilities.
